data.description: This spacious 6 bedroom, 5 bathroom home is located in the desirable Georgetown Village neighborhood. As you enter the home, you will be greeted by a grand foyer and formal dining area that leads into the open-concept living area. The living room features high ceilings, large windows, and a cozy fireplace.    The kitchen is a chef's dream with ample counter space, stainless steel appliances, and a center island. It also boasts a walk-in pantry and a breakfast nook that overlooks the backyard.     The primary suite is located on the main level and offers a luxurious retreat with a spa-like bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanity sinks. The primary suite also features a walk-in closet.    Upstairs, you will find four additional bedrooms, each with ample closet space and access to a bathroom. The extra bedroom downstairs   could easily be used as a home office, if desired. There is also a spacious game room, ideal for a playroom, and there is an additional media room!    The backyard of this home is truly a paradise. It features a huge grassy area and nice oaks for providing much needed shade in this Texas heat.     Dont miss out on this incredible opportunity as this home is priced very competitively for a quick sale!
